Create a cinematic scroll-based animation for a premium barbershop website.

Interaction concept:

As the user scrolls down, the main 3D barber character transitions smoothly through different camera angles and haircut stages, creating a dynamic storytelling experience.

Animation behavior:

Scroll Step 1 (top of page):

- Front angle

- Barber starting the haircut

- Subtle idle motion (breathing, cloth movement)

Scroll Step 2:

- Camera rotates slightly to the side (45 degrees)

- Clippers in motion

- Hair particles softly falling

- Light intensity increases slightly

Scroll Step 3:

- Top view cinematic angle

- Focus on fade precision

- Background slightly blurred (depth of field shift)

Scroll Step 4:

- Close-up shot

- Sharp details of haircut line

- Smooth slow-motion effect

Scroll Step 5:

- Final reveal

- Client finished haircut

- Barber steps back

- Soft glow lighting + premium feel

Animation style:

- Ultra smooth transitions (ease-in-out)

- Soft, clean animations (no harsh cuts)

- Cinematic blending between frames

- Subtle motion blur

Technical feel:

- Inspired by Apple product pages + Nike interactive sites

- Scroll-driven timeline animation (GSAP / Three.js / WebGL)

Extra UI interactions:

- Text fades in/out based on scroll

- CTA button subtly pulses

- Sections appear with smooth upward motion

Mood:

Immersive, premium, interactive storytelling.

Goal:

Make the user feel like they are inside the barbershop experience while scrolling.

